{"tid":1680021,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"[醫護和理非同我入黎] 點解黑警咁高人工？","createTime":"2019-10-28T14:15:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-28T22:55:50.000Z","uid":195944,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"fd7c1ce2fa55b03020ba276968d77e80570b59e0","tid":1680021,"uid":195944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T14:15:24.000Z","msg":"克警同普通政府工有唔同scale<br />\n佢地又唔係專業又唔做野 憑咩攞咁高人工？<br />\n<br />\n你地就唔同喇 掌握生死 以命搏命 但到頭黎得唔到相應人工？<br />\n公平？<br />\n<br />\n克警咁好bargaining power就係夠惡夠人多夠大聲<br />\n今年克警又檢討個scale喇 政府一定加佢地人工<br />\n<br />\n你地呢？ 護士醫生只跟hgps 醫管局完全唔當你地係專業, 但佢地高層就好似私人公司咁有bonus分無scale跟 <br />\n公平？<br />\n<br />\n唉 人善被人欺<br />\n醫護！反抗！<br />\n醫護做野唔駛你教！<br />\n專業道德係某啲狗無嘅野！<br />\n<br />\n有無方法可以話俾高層聽 我地士氣都好低 我地都好惡 我地都好多人？<br />\n加人工個個都有份 應該可以團結最多人<br />\n護士醫生有唔知咩聯會 治療師營養師應該都有屬會 可唔可以團結啲呀？<br />\n<br />\n利申東區醫院<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">保安<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"c8dcdf7eacba0a50001079ad1a09e3603df579e3","tid":1680021,"uid":195944,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T14:28:33.000Z","msg":"督察 $42000<br />\n註冊護士 $32000<br />\n<br />\n高級督察 $72000<br />\nAPN $55000<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n總督察 $87000<br />\nWM $60000<br />\n<br />\n警司 $112000<br />\nDOM $84000<br />\n<br />\nFYI"},{"pid":"e898642117b2f1dda0977fe3e72d5dd6f530e2e3","tid":1680021,"uid":195944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T14:31:14.000Z","msg":"無人為自己人工謀福利？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8d4917f10f836bac91a1fdf1b065315f0cfea67","tid":1680021,"uid":322974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c8dcdf7eacba0a50001079ad1a09e3603df579e3","tid":1680021,"uid":195944,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T14:28:33.000Z","msg":"督察 $42000<br />\n註冊護士 $32000<br />\n<br />\n高級督察 $72000<br />\n